Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.00,0:00:06.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,配备着以计算机为导航系统的赛车
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.94,0:00:09.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「高智能方程式」正式登场
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.94,0:00:09.24,Tips,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(416.667,656.667)}Cyber Formula
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.24,0:00:13.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,代替「F-1」的21世纪赛车
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.00,0:00:15.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令全世界的人都狂热起来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.11,0:00:33.57,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur0.333\bord0.333}我会马上赶过去的　已经不用担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.57,0:00:40.11,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur0.333\bord0.333}我会帮助你　因为我爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.98,0:00:43.73,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur0.333\bord0.333}不可思议的一阵不安
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.01,0:00:47.49,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur0.333\bord0.333}是你传来的SOS
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.72,0:00:53.62,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur0.333\bord0.333}从昨夜开始就一直感觉得到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.63,0:01:00.10,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur0.333\bord0.333}突如其来的暴风雨阻挡了前进的路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.35,0:01:04.03,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur0.333\bord0.333}心头浮起不祥的预感
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.10,0:01:08.95,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur0.333\bord0.333}说是爱也好奇迹也好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.51,0:01:15.01,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur0.333\bord0.333}可不能被当作笨蛋　不论什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.01,0:01:20.77,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur0.333\bord0.333}就算又掀起了一股新的波澜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.24,0:01:27.81,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur0.333\bord0.333}现在就马上赶过去　就在那里等我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.81,0:01:33.56,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur0.333\bord0.333}守护那个梦想直到永远
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.56,0:01:36.73,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur0.333\bord0.333}是你的话一定可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.18,0:01:43.73,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur0.333\bord0.333}我会马上赶过去的　已经不用担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.73,0:01:50.46,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur0.333\bord0.333}我会帮助你　因为我如此爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.17,0:02:07.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正当隼人从世界锦标赛第一战的\N失败阴影中走出来时
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.56,0:02:09.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布里德加贺出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.17,0:02:11.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并邀请隼人一起参加比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.98,0:02:16.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是由一群将生命置之度外的赛车手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.45,0:02:18.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所参加的非正式对战车赛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.99,0:02:21.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这场比赛里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.44,0:02:23.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隼人从加贺身上学到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.17,0:02:26.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己所欠缺的随机应变的本领
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.87,0:02:30.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赛车就是战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.73,0:02:32.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是男人赌上生命的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.13,0:02:40.13,Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(477.333,496.667)}{\blur0.667\bord0.667}青春的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.30,0:02:51.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秘鲁的高地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.88,0:02:53.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玻利维亚高原的山岳跑道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.54,0:02:55.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这被称为是蝎子根源地的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.50,0:02:58.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海尼尔、古德利安、罗贝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.40,0:02:59.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陆续飞驰而过
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.47,0:03:03.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接着是今年首次登场的卡明格斯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.66,0:03:04.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.74,0:03:06.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡明格斯打滑了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.47,0:03:09.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,传说要是不小心踩到蝎子的巢穴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.19,0:03:10.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就可能招致死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.41,0:03:13.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡明格斯彷佛中了这道诅咒一般
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.17,0:03:14.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成为了这个高原的牺牲者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.93,0:03:17.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,组长
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.03,0:03:19.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来阿斯拉达有必要做改装呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.65,0:03:20.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.39,0:03:22.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是时候展现我们维修技师的实力了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.75,0:03:24.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总教练
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.63,0:03:26.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去年的资料已经全部看完了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.76,0:03:27.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.72,0:03:29.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为阿斯拉达需要进行改装作业
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.36,0:03:31.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,改装是指…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.04,0:03:33.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次比赛的场地在秘鲁高原
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.86,0:03:35.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是以越野道路为主的赛道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.42,0:03:38.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在海拔4000公尺的高原上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.48,0:03:39.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空气也非常稀薄
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.17,0:03:41.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,引擎和其他系统
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.23,0:03:42.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都必须针对特性做改装
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.65,0:03:45.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隼人 这次的改装
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.33,0:03:46.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对会让你刮目相看的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.01,0:03:48.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好期待一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.86,0:03:52.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来他们十分投入啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.28,0:03:54.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎是相当困难的场地哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.00,0:03:56.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隼人你没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.44,0:03:57.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.66,0:03:59.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要从现在开始就吓我嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.08,0:03:59.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总教练
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.16,0:04:03.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进入墨西哥国境就要进行试跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.76,0:04:04.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.80,0:04:06.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从一场比赛结束的瞬间开始
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.82,0:04:08.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一场比赛就已经开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.44,0:04:18.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在隼人及菅生阿斯拉达车队一行人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.97,0:04:21.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正朝着世界杯锦标赛第二战的舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.32,0:04:22.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,南美的秘鲁前进
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.33,0:04:50.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太酷了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.00,0:04:54.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新搭载的部件可以完美应对\N秘鲁的山岳跑道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.44,0:04:57.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,底盘的重量比以前重一点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.39,0:04:59.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但车体的平衡性并没因此改变
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.56,0:05:00.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.04,0:05:02.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当地资料整理的部分
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.73,0:05:04.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请再给我一点时间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.33,0:05:05.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在还不急
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.52,0:05:06.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多花点时间准备吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.05,0:05:07.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.47,0:05:10.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备开始试跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.01,0:05:10.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.24,0:05:15.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.41,0:05:16.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微感觉到车身重量变重了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.89,0:05:19.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这并不会影响到驾驶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.62,0:05:22.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,改装后让我有了重生的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.35,0:05:25.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想不到你还会说这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.47,0:05:27.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上坡左弯道 注意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.07,0:05:28.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.10,0:05:32.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.36,0:05:33.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,引擎状态不错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.63,0:05:35.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现标高是2800公尺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.91,0:05:37.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到极限区域之前想再好好跑一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.16,0:05:39.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要太勉强哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.41,0:05:39.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.38,0:05:43.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对向来车 急速接近
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.77,0:05:53.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.12,0:05:57.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,避开货车后却撞上了仙人掌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.73,0:05:59.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要注意一点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.07,0:06:00.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这地区的土块因为空气干燥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.64,0:06:02.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常坚硬 撞上可不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.25,0:06:02.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.52,0:06:04.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,良平
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.04,0:06:07.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后扰流翼稍微歪了 调整一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.50,0:06:07.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.40,0:06:10.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大约向左2毫米
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.05,0:06:13.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烤肉已经快好了 大家来吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.41,0:06:15.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美琪 先吃饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.96,0:06:17.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我等一下再吃就好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.74,0:06:19.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们先吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.65,0:06:20.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.66,0:06:22.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们就先去吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.25,0:06:23.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.04,0:06:24.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们就先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.89,0:06:26.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,组长也先去吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.09,0:06:27.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.51,0:06:38.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是虫子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.59,0:06:40.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是只小虫也可能破坏车体的平衡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.00,0:06:44.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个还真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.60,0:06:45.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过就是烤个肉嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.97,0:06:47.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么简单谁不会
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.31,0:06:49.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还真敢说啊 隼人的份没收
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.65,0:06:50.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 怎么这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.07,0:06:54.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,良平 吃那么多肉对身体不好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.02,0:06:56.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快喝点水
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.58,0:06:59.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次别吃那么快了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.13,0:07:01.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢款待
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.39,0:07:03.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经吃饱了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.43,0:07:05.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要把所有地方都再确认一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.97,0:07:07.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相当的慎重呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.38,0:07:10.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为无法成为第一战的战力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.69,0:07:12.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而产生了补偿心理吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.09,0:07:18.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好锁紧了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.21,0:07:21.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 顺便换换大灯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.01,0:07:29.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星星真漂亮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.31,0:07:32.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.31,0:07:32.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.27,0:07:37.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像伸手就能摸到一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.23,0:07:46.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的父母绝对不会有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.88,0:07:49.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么突然说起这个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.74,0:07:52.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青梅竹马在想什么事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.08,0:07:53.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一下子就看透了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.24,0:08:00.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界杯锦标赛的第二战
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.18,0:08:01.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我无论如何都要赢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.00,0:08:04.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们看到新闻一定会来见我的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.44,0:08:06.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说的也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.84,0:08:11.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对要拿下优胜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.28,0:08:20.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直线前进的安定性良好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.34,0:08:23.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接着要测试过弯特性了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.39,0:08:23.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.38,0:08:27.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.37,0:08:30.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿斯拉达
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.67,0:08:33.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,方向盘出现细微偏差的原因是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.88,0:08:38.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,传动控制系统在硬件机能及软件方面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.84,0:08:39.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都没有异常
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.16,0:08:41.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有异常…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.57,0:08:43.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但确实有向外偏移的现象
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.32,0:08:46.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在左转时是正常的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.05,0:08:51.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然只有在右转弯时会出现
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.40,0:08:52.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是转向不足的反应
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.40,0:08:52.49,Tips,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(456.667,656.667)}Understeer
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.82,0:08:54.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是外部因素的影响导致
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.23,0:08:56.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是风吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.07,0:09:01.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反方向跑一次就知道是不是风的影响了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.45,0:09:08.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然在右转时会转向不足
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.91,0:09:10.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是风的影响
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.36,0:09:12.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有异常现象
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.47,0:09:14.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为求慎重 也更换了相关零件
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.82,0:09:16.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主动式悬吊系统、油缸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.81,0:09:19.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机油帮浦、传动轴、悬吊臂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.28,0:09:22.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到目前为止 没有任何的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.55,0:09:23.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接着还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.29,0:09:32.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经都过了三个小时了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.23,0:09:33.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.78,0:09:38.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.07,0:09:42.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,车子没有异常
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.52,0:09:44.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这不可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.57,0:09:46.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,计算机方面也已经检查过了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.38,0:09:48.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,程序完全正常
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.48,0:09:53.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不应该是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.22,0:09:57.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在右转时确实会转向不足
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.75,0:09:59.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若真如此 也不会是车子的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.47,0:10:03.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的能够这么断言吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.98,0:10:07.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能产生问题的地方 我们全检查过了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.81,0:10:08.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对没有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.20,0:10:12.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至今右转时从没出现过转向不足
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.41,0:10:14.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一定是整备上的失误
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.44,0:10:16.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在整备上可是费尽了心力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.97,0:10:18.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,区区一个车手懂些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.82,0:10:19.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.29,0:10:27.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两个都别再吵了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.04,0:10:28.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,团队的伙伴之间在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.71,0:10:34.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要再试跑一次进行确认
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.86,0:10:40.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在将双手固定在方向盘正中央
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.61,0:10:41.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就快到右转弯了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.96,0:10:43.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样在还没找到真正原因前 太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.20,0:10:45.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非得查明是我的技术有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.58,0:10:47.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是有别的原因不可
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.06,0:10:53.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然还是出现了转向不足的反应
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.83,0:10:56.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,测定器上并没有任何异常现象
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.96,0:10:59.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的偏移现象是真实存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.65,0:11:01.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种异状还是第一次出现
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.76,0:11:03.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别把原因归咎到车子上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.26,0:11:04.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整备是完美的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.69,0:11:05.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你技术的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.12,0:11:07.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才没有那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.55,0:11:08.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前方出现障碍物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.20,0:11:09.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.11,0:11:16.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.90,0:11:35.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.66,0:11:39.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.10,0:11:42.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有没有受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.45,0:11:44.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隼人…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.66,0:12:04.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎能听见车子们的哭泣声
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.05,0:12:06.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简直就像是车子的坟场
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.75,0:12:08.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,良平
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.22,0:12:10.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果整备上真有问题的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.73,0:12:13.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和阿斯拉达都可能葬身于此的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.72,0:12:15.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果车手本身的技术就有问题呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.16,0:12:24.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自信心固然相当重要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.27,0:12:26.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但人不可能是完美的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.01,0:12:28.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,车田叔…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.32,0:12:32.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在以前也遇过同样的状况
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.92,0:12:37.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算起来也已经是三十年前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.21,0:12:43.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隼人的爸爸 风见广之
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.21,0:12:45.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和明日香的爸爸 菅生幸二郎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.93,0:12:48.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时都还只是高中生而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.62,0:12:50.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,源叔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.53,0:12:52.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们赛车已经设计出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.02,0:12:53.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是风见设计的蓝图
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.59,0:12:56.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能为我们指点一下吗 拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.88,0:13:12.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这只是会跑的棺材吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.47,0:13:18.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 开始工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.14,0:13:21.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 今天不帮忙了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.42,0:13:24.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 马上就开始工作
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.16,0:13:25.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.43,0:13:27.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请让我帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.73,0:13:28.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我什么都愿意做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.84,0:13:30.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等将来时机成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.17,0:13:31.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请让我们利用这里的废弃材料
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.82,0:13:34.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,制造属于我们自己的赛车
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.76,0:13:37.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先把那边的东西整理一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.26,0:13:38.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.40,0:13:45.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时的我们虽然没有钱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.72,0:13:50.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却拥有制造属于自己赛车的美丽梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.23,0:13:58.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一遍又一遍的修改设计图
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.69,0:14:00.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并请源叔给我们指导
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.52,0:14:03.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.50,0:14:06.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾是F-1赛车维修技师的源叔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.19,0:14:08.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却始终没有点头
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.83,0:14:19.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风见 你终于做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.90,0:14:22.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这部车肯定是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.75,0:14:25.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能跑得跟风一样快的赛车
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.24,0:14:27.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风见 成功了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.04,0:14:29.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于得到源叔的认可了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.67,0:14:34.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.36,0:14:39.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在源叔的同意下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.93,0:14:43.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们利用了工厂里的废弃材料
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.46,0:14:47.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来制造我们期待已久的赛车
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.04,0:14:56.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于 承载我们青春梦想的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.92,0:14:58.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乘风一号诞生了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.83,0:15:03.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们经过了无数次的测试
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.00,0:15:12.90,neta2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fscx0\pos(10,13.333)\t(0,200,1,\fscx100)\t(5300,0,1,\fscx0)}————
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.74,0:15:10.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而 在FJ1600比赛将至之期
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.30,0:15:12.60,neta1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\move(10,13.333,10,6.667,0,200)\pos(10,6.667)\fad(300,300)}FJ1600
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.30,0:15:12.60,neta3,NTP,0,0,0,,{\move(10,13.333,10,33.333,0,200)\pos(10,33.333)\fad(300,300)}日本方程式赛车的一种。\N一般认为 FJ 是 Formula Junior 的简称，即青年方程式。(也有 Formula Japan 的说法存在)\N对于卡丁车手来说，FJ1600赛车是开始方程式赛车生涯的入门车型，1600为发动机排气量\N1600c.c的规格标示。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.70,0:15:12.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后的测试当中…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.15,0:15:26.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菅生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.44,0:15:28.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧 菅生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.42,0:15:30.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.25,0:15:31.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.47,0:15:35.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撞成这个样子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.28,0:15:36.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岂不是要报销了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.05,0:15:38.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原因出在你的整备上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.93,0:15:39.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.24,0:15:41.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在撞车之前的直线道上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.49,0:15:43.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悬吊系统就已经发出异音了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.69,0:15:46.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这是在质疑我的整备功力吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.95,0:15:48.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在每次出车之前都会做彻底的检查
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.59,0:15:51.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道不是你驾驶上的失误吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.60,0:15:53.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有驾驶失误
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.39,0:15:56.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一辆整备完善的赛车…会撞毁的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.65,0:15:57.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只会是因为驾驶失误了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.06,0:16:01.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不想死在你那过剩的自信心下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.79,0:16:03.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.91,0:16:05.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手啊你们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.99,0:16:07.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷静一点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.38,0:16:13.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是我们将乘风一号完全拆解
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.52,0:16:15.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仔细检查肇事的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.76,0:16:17.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但终究找不到任何缺陷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.77,0:16:21.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然…是我的失误吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.34,0:16:23.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们几个过来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.95,0:16:28.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差速器…怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.95,0:16:28.46,Tips,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(394.667,656.667)}Differential Gear
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.34,0:16:35.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.02,0:16:36.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.43,0:16:38.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种地方竟然会有石头
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.10,0:16:40.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 为什么石头会…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.81,0:16:43.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕是在更换齿轮油时掉进去的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.12,0:16:46.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我当时吓了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.00,0:16:49.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由于自己的失误
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.06,0:16:52.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差点就赔上了好友菅生幸二郎的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.99,0:16:55.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 菅生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.40,0:16:57.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,车田
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.10,0:16:59.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从今天开始…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.93,0:17:02.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我再也不碰任何车子了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.97,0:17:05.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.61,0:17:06.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若不是有你…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.71,0:17:10.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也无法实现成为赛车手的梦想了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.93,0:17:13.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维修技师哪里都可以找到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.84,0:17:15.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经没办法再继续下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.32,0:17:17.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,车田…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.19,0:17:19.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下啊车田
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.21,0:17:23.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逃走了不就承认自己被打败了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.68,0:17:28.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果扼杀了好朋友的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.88,0:17:30.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以后要怎么面对你自己
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.67,0:17:42.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,车田…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.57,0:17:46.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,车田
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.78,0:17:58.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我过去曾经因为整备上的失误
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.74,0:18:00.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,害死了我最好的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.51,0:18:03.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从此之后 我便开始用那个放大镜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.81,0:18:06.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来调查车辆发生事故的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.95,0:18:10.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是现在每当我在修车的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.14,0:18:12.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总彷佛听到车子的叹息声
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.82,0:18:14.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为它们大部份都是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.91,0:18:16.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为粗暴驾驶而撞毁的车子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.85,0:18:20.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者是不被爱惜而废弃的车子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.98,0:18:25.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我已经不再需要那个放大镜了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.82,0:18:27.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,车田 这个就送给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.71,0:18:30.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.42,0:18:33.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会用一生好好保存的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.62,0:18:42.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到今天 它仍是我最重要的宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.50,0:18:47.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总教练 请把它借给我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.29,0:18:56.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也可能不是整备上的失误
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.45,0:18:58.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若是如此就得向他们道歉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.58,0:19:05.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,方向盘部件全部没有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.77,0:19:07.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来 悬吊系统也要检查
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.06,0:19:08.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.72,0:19:10.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每一块零件每一颗螺丝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.88,0:19:13.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,传感器组件和齿轮类…等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.05,0:19:14.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能拆下来的 全都得拆下来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.50,0:19:18.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要彻底的调查真正原因
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.95,0:19:26.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经五个小时了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.27,0:19:28.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道问题真的在我身上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.79,0:19:29.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若真是如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.22,0:19:40.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,视力没有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.99,0:19:51.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.17,0:20:00.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是脏东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.34,0:20:00.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.34,0:20:05.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.06,0:20:08.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,良平
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.62,0:20:17.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美琪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.95,0:20:18.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.15,0:20:21.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总教练 原因出在扭力分配
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.15,0:20:21.36,Tips,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(645.333,656.667)} Torque Split
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.44,0:20:21.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.67,0:20:26.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在G传感器的雷射发射镜片上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.83,0:20:28.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发现了脏东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.69,0:20:30.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么小的一个脏污…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.69,0:20:32.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连计算机都没有办法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.06,0:20:34.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,测出这个微小异物的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.55,0:20:36.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这个异物的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.54,0:20:38.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使得扭力的前后分配失去均衡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.36,0:20:39.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才导致了转向不足的发生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.84,0:20:42.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我们维修技师的失误
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.43,0:20:46.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.87,0:20:49.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,组长
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.95,0:20:51.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你给我住口
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.91,0:20:54.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身为整备团队组长的我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.80,0:20:57.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疏于检查 是我的责任
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.44,0:21:00.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美琪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.32,0:21:02.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是组长的错
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.52,0:21:04.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我的过失
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.14,0:21:10.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隼人 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.57,0:21:14.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请站起来吧 美琪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.82,0:21:16.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,良平也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.70,0:21:19.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻烦你们再做一次整备工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.05,0:21:24.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的性命就交给你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.20,0:21:36.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.59,0:21:38.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这还是第一次感觉大家是个团队
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.51,0:21:40.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.97,0:21:43.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,团队合作不是成员们相处融洽而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.05,0:21:47.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是为了保护彼此而努力决胜的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.24,0:21:50.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来的秘鲁杯锦标赛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.17,0:21:51.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们要抱着如此的决胜之心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.68,0:21:53.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奋力一战
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.01,0:21:55.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天很早就要出发了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.26,0:21:57.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶快去准备吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.48,0:21:58.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.79,0:22:16.85,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur0.333\bord0.333}人们的视线追不上他的背影
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.44,0:22:27.16,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur0.333\bord0.333}是因为有要向前迈进的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.77,0:22:30.27,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur0.333\bord0.333}believe each other
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.27,0:22:37.05,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur0.333\bord0.333}停下双手　仰望天空的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.74,0:22:40.17,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur0.333\bord0.333}believe each other
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.17,0:22:48.90,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur0.333\bord0.333}你的笑容就是我心灵的支柱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.58,0:22:55.84,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur0.333\bord0.333}正因为现在是如此辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.84,0:23:00.34,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur0.333\bord0.333}明日才会闪耀灿烂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.34,0:23:05.85,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur0.333\bord0.333}所以我不会后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.85,0:23:11.50,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur0.333\bord0.333}自己所选择的终点
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.79,0:23:16.27,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur0.333\bord0.333}来吧　随风奔跑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.27,0:23:21.37,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur0.333\bord0.333}总有一天　我们会成为胜利者
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.98,0:23:30.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在赛前的预备休息时间里
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.45,0:23:32.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,粉丝们总是相当热情的追逐着车手偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.32,0:23:35.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是高智能方程式的粉丝吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.72,0:23:36.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.76,0:23:39.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然说不想要中途退场的赛车手签名
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.40,0:23:41.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还真敢说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.58,0:23:42.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 来做个约定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.83,0:23:44.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对会站上颁奖台给你看的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.93,0:23:48.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新世纪GPX 高智能方程式
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.25,0:23:50.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与少女的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.33,0:23:53.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一集也相当有趣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.36,0:23:54.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Red Zone！
